title: #100: 100% With Sam and Ryan
description: Welcome to the 100th episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli.  This episode Sam and Ryan look back at 100 episode and discuss the future.  Thank you for all for your support on the last 100 and hopefully another killer 100 in the future.
